Wideband statistics:

Data flow:

  Input pass:
    input IP with right DSCP delivered to WB receive buffer: docsis_ip_cnt
    if UDP not mapped to QAM, drop IP: docsis_drop_ip_cnt
    if QAM has not started, drop IP: docsis_qam_inactive_cnt
    parse each TP within IP: docsis_tp_cnt
    if sync loss, drop all TPs from current till end of IP: docsis_syncloss_cnt
    if null TP, drop TP: docsis_null_tp_cnt
    check for input overrun: docsis_overrun_cnt

  Output pass:
    schedule all output TP ()

