To fake a NB CM to register as a WB CM:

test cable wb on    : this command is not savable
(Or this instead: test cable wb reg on)
conf t
int c6/0/4
cable wb <channel_id>

NOTE: channel_id must be the cable downstream channel-id set up for
      one of the WB interface (eg C3/0/0:0), otherwise the image will crash!

After that, reset the cable modems.  They will then come up as WB.

